<p><a name="New_Year_dates" id="New_Year_dates"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Chinese_New_Year&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: New Year dates">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">New Year dates</span></h2>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Chinese_Astrology" title="Chinese Astrology" class="mw-redirect">Chinese Astrology</a></div>
<table class="wikitable" border="1" style="float:left; margin-left:1.5em;">
