<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Chinese_New_Year&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Icons and ornamentals">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Icons and ornamentals</span></h3>
